    "description": "《修罗》是一款以独特连招为主打的横板砍杀游戏。这里没有高性能的霸道怪物和丰富的关卡地图。玩家所能做的是不断对自身的磨练，在一条通往家园的道路上，防守消灭进犯的怪物潮。并且玩家不能只是直白的将敌人击败，需通过自身所掌握的各种技巧获取高连招评价，来尽可能压榨出敌人身上的资源和宝物，以保证能应付接下来的挑战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >心如止水，克敌制胜</h2>连招水平的高低，关键在于对怒意的控制，怒意进阶成功除了能让玩家攻击速度变快，提升连招爽快感和增加更多招式衔接可能性，还会使玩家更容易获得高连招评价，但是进阶失败也会有相应的代价。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/8e785006b212b5508785264c565aae2a.poster.avif?t=1770641112\" width=630 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/8e785006b212b5508785264c565aae2a.webm?t=1770641112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/8e785006b212b5508785264c565aae2a.mp4?t=1770641112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各式武技，齐集于身</h2>玩家不仅能升级解锁特定的技能，同时能从战场上获得各种类型的武技进行研习，并且还能通过武技领悟出强大的奥义。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/b9432e38d49e29e7a3bd5896e1427ad3.poster.avif?t=1770641112\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/b9432e38d49e29e7a3bd5896e1427ad3.webm?t=1770641112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/b9432e38d49e29e7a3bd5896e1427ad3.mp4?t=1770641112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >巧妙组合，引发潜力</h2>配饰与魂器存在元素羁绊，搭配得当便能激发魂器特殊属性，助你势如破竹。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/6bd56db9c698f91c5152215cf72b7d5f.poster.avif?t=1770641112\" width=630 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/6bd56db9c698f91c5152215cf72b7d5f.webm?t=1770641112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/6bd56db9c698f91c5152215cf72b7d5f.mp4?t=1770641112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >运筹帷幄，掌控局势</h2>把握好每次战斗结束的部署，能力升级，技能研习，装备调整，休养生息......每一步都对战局的趋势变化有关键意义。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/676a2595b45313da91d9d01f425014fc.poster.avif?t=1770641112\" width=630 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/676a2595b45313da91d9d01f425014fc.webm?t=1770641112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/676a2595b45313da91d9d01f425014fc.mp4?t=1770641112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >研习技巧，突破挑战</h2>玩家战后能在练功台中进行不同的技巧学习，并且会随机出现不同奖励的技巧任务，供玩家挑战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/3fd11b4bd3ca4aacc85c71ad1c874088.poster.avif?t=1770641112\" width=630 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/3fd11b4bd3ca4aacc85c71ad1c874088.webm?t=1770641112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364910/extras/3fd11b4bd3ca4aacc85c71ad1c874088.mp4?t=1770641112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
